highlights.text: Arijit Singh has the most spots on Top Songs Lucknow. Kesariya is the highest at #1.
Tu Aake Dekhle by King has been on Top Songs Lucknow the longest, at 52 weeks straight.
Lemonade by Diljit Dosanjh is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Lucknow, up 20 spots at #56.
Jaane Kyu Main by Prashant Katheriya is the highest new entry on Top Songs Lucknow at #63.
